The paper discusses techniques for efficient and effective big data analytics, which are relevant to several sub-categories in computer science. cs.DB (Databases) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on data processing and analytics. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper discusses approximation algorithms. cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are relevant as the paper discusses techniques for processing and analyzing large amounts of data. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also relevant as the paper discusses techniques for optimizing computation.
